---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-950 border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 mt-auto">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-10">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start md:items-center gap-6">

      <div>
        <span class="text-xl font-extrabold text-orange-500">Vekteren</span>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mt-1 max-w-xs">
          Vektnedgang som faktisk fungerer – ingen mirakelkurer, bare vitenskap og tålmodighet.
        </p>
      </div>

      <nav class="flex flex-wrap gap-x-6 gap-y-2 text-sm">
        <a href="/fremgang" class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-orange-500 transition-colors">Min fremgang</a>
        <a href="/kalorier" class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-orange-500 transition-colors">Kalorier</a>
        <a href="/mat" class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-orange-500 transition-colors">Mat</a>
        <a href="/trening" class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-orange-500 transition-colors">Trening</a>
